  "description": "A low-angle, long exposure photograph captures a dramatic scene of a bridge spanning a body of water, likely a bay or ocean. The bridge, appearing as a dark silhouette against a bright, hazy sky, is the dominant architectural element.  Strong wakes or waves from a moving boat or ship cut across the foreground, creating dynamic lines and texture in the water. The sun is prominently featured, creating a radiant glow and lens flare. In the distant background, faint outlines of industrial structures or buildings can be seen along the shoreline. The water transitions from foamy white near the camera to a calmer, shimmering blue-gray further out. The overall effect is one of motion, power, and scale.",
